reviewText: I ordered the movie set it off and I ended up with a trailer on some bikers, very disappointed
Was not what I had asked for. Wanted Set it off with Queen latifa!
We thought we were renting the movie "set it off."  You should look at the way this clip was advertised.  We would never have rented this clip.

Rented this movie as Amazon listed as the real feature film Set It Off, not a bunch of douche bags acting stupid on their little motorcycles.

Don't rent this if you think this is for the real feature film Set IT Off

Hey Amazon, False advertising!

Why don't you refund me my money?
